    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Using the Pebble accelerometer</para>
<para>The AccelerometerService enables the Pebble accelerometer to detect taps, perform measures at a given frequency, and transmit samples in batches to save CPU time and processing.</para>
<para>For available code samples, see the <ulink url="https://github.com/pebble-examples/feature-accel-discs/">feature-accel-discs</ulink> example app. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
